text: Nathaniel Cornelius "Nate" Robinson (born May 31, 1984 in Seattle, Washington) is an American professional basketball player. In 2012, he started playing for the Chicago Bulls. He played for the New York Knicks, for the Boston Celtics, for the Oklahoma City Thunder, and for the Golden State Warriors. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:3x3 basketball players Category:African-American basketball players Category:American basketball players Category:American football cornerbacks Category:Boston Celtics players Category:Businesspeople from California Category:Businesspeople from Seattle Category:Chicago Bulls players Category:Denver Nuggets players Category:Golden State Warriors players Category:Los Angeles Clippers players Category:New Orleans Pelicans players Category:New York Knicks players Category:Oklahoma City Thunder players Category:People from Alameda County, California Category:Point guards Category:Sportspeople from Seattle
